org.modelio.vcore.smkernel

Interface ISmMeta

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    SmObjectImpl

    public interface ISmMeta
    This interface defines the methods that SmObjectImpl must implement in order to deal with SmAttribute and SmDependency. It actually defines the generic API to a metaclass features.
    Author:
    phv
